{"word":"σκηπτός","slug":"σκηπτός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>σκηπτός</b></el> <el>(σκηπτός, οῦ, ὁ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:σκήπτω'><el>σκήπτω</el></a>\n<p/><i>a thunder-bolt</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:— <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> of pestilence, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>; of war, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/>"}]}